  follow-up cron-register absorbed via hive init (raw 99 launchd-standalone ban) - daily scan of design/kick/<date>_*_omega_cycle.json + state/discovery_absorption/registry.jsonl drift detection
  follow-up cross-project propagation via raw 47 - sister repos (hive own / n6-architecture / hexa-lang / anima / airgenome) adopt parallel finding-absorption mandate
